            <h3 class="subtitle">For dogs with style that goes on and on! </h3>
            <p>We're a cozy little pet salon with a big heart, dedicated to making your furry best friends look and feel amazing.</p>
            <p>From bubbly baths to fresh haircuts and belly rubs in between, we make grooming a fun and stress-free experience. </p>
            <%= image_tag 'long-body.svg', alt: 'Long body dachshund bg', class: 'img-long-dach' %>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%# Flow Section %>
    <div id="flow_1">
        <h1 class="section-title">Flow</h1>
        <div class="flow-container">
